sources.description:
Movie Class HOLIDAY Edition!
Stars: Van Johnson, Lori Nelson, Claude Rains, Jim Backus
Director: Bretaigne Windust
A 12th Century legend comes to vivid life in this TECHNICOLOR TV musical. Somewhere in Niedersachsen, the town of Hamelin is overrun with rats. Who do you call? The Pied Piper of course!  But after working his musically magic and ridding Hamelin of its rodents, he is doubled crossed by the townâ€™s avaricious Major! Watch for Van Johnson in a dual role.
